quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  27,82,WE ‘IDHA WEKA’AL-KAWLU ‘ALEJHIM ‘EHREXHNA LEHUM DABBETEN MINEL-’ERDI TUKELLIMUHUM ‘ENNE EN-NASE KANU BI’AJATINA LA JUKINUNE
  27,83,WE JEWME NEHSHURU MIN KULLI ‘UMMETIN FEWXHÆN MIMMEN JUKEDHDHIBU BI’AJATINA FEHUM JUZA’UNE
  27,84,HETTA ‘IDHA XHA’U KALE ‘EKEDHDHEBTUM BI’AJATI WE LEM TUHITU BIHA ‘ILMÆN ‘EMMADHA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  27,85,WE WEKA’AL-KAWLU ‘ALEJHIM BIMA DHELEMU FEHUM LA JENTIKUNE
  27,86,‘ELEM JEREW ‘ENNA XHE’ALNAL-LEJLE LIJESKUNU FIHI WE EN-NEHARE MUBSIRÆN ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JU’UMINUNE
  27,87,WE JEWME JUNFEHU FI ES-SURI FEFEZI’A MEN FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MEN FIL-’ERDI ‘ILLA MEN SHA’EL-LAHU WE KULLUN ‘ETEWHU DAHIRINE
  27,88,WE TERAL-XHIBALE TEHSEBUHA XHAMIDETEN WE HIJE TEMURRU MERRE ES-SEHABI SUN’A ELLAHIL-LEDHI ‘ETKANE KULLE SHEJ’IN ‘INNEHU HABIRUN BIMA TEF’ALUNE
  27,89,MEN XHA’E BIL-HESENETI FELEHU HAJRUN MINHA WE HUM MIN FEZA’IN JEWME’IDHIN ‘AMINUNE
  27,90,WE MEN XHA’E BIS-SEJJI’ETI FEKUBBET WUXHUHUHUM FI EN-NARI HEL TUXHZEWNE ‘ILLA MA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  27,91,‘INNEMA ‘UMIRTU ‘EN ‘A’BUDE REBBE HEDHIHIL-BELDETIL-LEDHI HERREMEHA WE LEHU KULLU SHEJ’IN WE ‘UMIRTU ‘EN ‘EKUNE MINEL-MUSLIMINE
  27,92,WE ‘EN ‘ETLUWEL-KUR’ANE FEMENI EHTEDA FE’INNEMA JEHTEDI LINEFSIHI WE MEN DELLE FEKUL ‘INNEMA ‘ENA MINEL-MUNDHIRINE
  27,93,WE KULIL-HEMDU LILLAHI SEJURIKUM ‘AJATIHI FETA’RIFUNEHA WE MA REBBUKE BIGAFILIN ‘AMMA TA’MELUNE
  28,1,TA-SIN-MIM
  28,2,TILKE ‘AJATUL-KITABIL-MUBINI
  28,3,NETLU ‘ALEJKE MIN NEBE’I MUSA WE FIR’AWNE BIL-HEKKI LIKAWMIN JU’UMINUNE
  28,4,‘INNE FIR’AWNE ‘ALA FIL-’ERDI WE XHE’ALE ‘EHLEHA SHIJA’ÆN JESTED’IFU TA’IFETEN MINHUM JUDHEBBIHU ‘EBNA’EHUM WE JESTEHJI NISA’EHUM ‘INNEHU KANE MINEL-MUFSIDINE
  28,5,WE NURIDU ‘EN NEMUNNE ‘ALEL-LEDHINE ESTUD’IFU FIL-’ERDI WE NEXH’ALEHUM ‘E’IMMETEN WE NEXH’ALEHUMUL-WARITHINE
  28,6,WE NUMEKKINE LEHUM FIL-’ERDI WE NURIJE FIR’AWNE WE HAMANE WE XHUNUDEHUMA MINHUM MA KANU JEHDHERUNE
  28,7,WE ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILA ‘UMMI MUSA ‘EN ‘ERDI’IHI FE’IDHA HIFTI ‘ALEJHI FE’ELKIHI FIL-JEMMI WE LA TEHAFI WE LA TEHZENI ‘INNA RADDUHU ‘ILEJKI WE XHA’ILUHU MINEL-MURSELINE
  28,8,FALTEKATEHU ‘ALU FIR’AWNE LIJEKUNE LEHUM ‘ADUWÆN WE HEZENÆN ‘INNE FIR’AWNE WE HAMANE WE XHUNUDEHUMA KANU HATI’INE
  28,9,WE KALET EMRE’ETU FIR’AWNE KURRETU ‘AJNIN LI WE LEKE LA TEKTULUHU ‘ASA ‘EN JENFE’ANA ‘EW NETTEHIDHEHU WELEDÆN WE HUM LA JESH’URUNE
  28,10,WE ‘ESBEHE FU’UADU ‘UMMI MUSA FARIGÆN ‘IN KADET LETUBDI BIHI LEWLA ‘EN REBETNA ‘ALA KALBIHA LITEKUNE MINEL-MU’UMININE
  28,11,WE KALET LI’HTIHI KUSSIHI FEBESURET BIHI ‘AN XHUNUBIN WE HUM LA JESH’URUNE